**File:** `recursion.php` (or the integrated `main.php`)

**What it does:**  
Simulates how book categories are organized into folders using a recursive function that prints each category and its books with proper indentation.

**Run it by:**  
Opening the PHP file in a browser or local server (e.g., `http://localhost/recursion.php`).

**Expected Output Example:**
Fiction
Fantasy
Harry Potter
The Hobbit
Mystery
Sherlock Holmes
Gone Girl
Non-Fiction
Science
A Brief History of Time
The Selfish Gene
Biography
Steve Jobs
Becoming
